N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 2 ยง 372.8 - Excess plan fund

State Regulations

Contributions to the plan shall be deposited in a separate
fund established and administered by the system. This fund is intended to be
exempt from Federal income tax under code sections 115 and
415(m)(1). Notes
